景建议，平台首先要严格落实自动续订、自动续费前 5 日提醒要求，如果不提醒，则视作不续订、不续费。此外，取消续费应该设置「一键功能」解决，且明确放在首页最明显的区域。不能开通收费容易，退订则层层设槛，操作复杂。「有的根本找不到退订的选项，有的退订按钮藏得很深、字体很小很浅。退订步骤复杂，以为退订了，实际上步骤没完成，仍有被自动扣除下一个周期费用的可能。」他对记者表示。聚焦两会｜互联网总让人一不小心就「踩坑」？这些建议事关消费者权益"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/a45379d33_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647466785"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwNCI2s7/xaYbEAMaCTEwNjE1ODg1NSCur6avBjAAOJoBQCRyCTY0NzQ2Njc4NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1709895999.199524", "card_id": "Q_639331795", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 77}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "扫兴式教育，会让孩子有多窒息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2a476c5a5b2c167ba9462766419c032_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/639331795"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwNCI2s7/xaYbEAMaCTEwNDM1MTczNyDRoYitBjAAOKYBQCVyCTYzOTMzMTc5NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1709895999.199767", "card_id": "Q_647544907", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 134}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些适合在女神节送给女神的数码产品？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8961a8a72b02dd21ac75c7f63f06aa81_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647544907"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwNCI2s7/xaYbEAMaCTEwNjE3NjE0NyCk5KmvBjAAOJoBQCZyCTY0NzU